02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.410 --> 02:50.000
[Episod 35]

02:51.000 --> 02:52.850
Jika saya benar-benar mahukan sesuatu,

02:52.900 --> 02:54.030
